# Design QA

Before completing a screen verify:

✓ Uses design tokens

✓ Uses reusable components

✓ Responsive

✓ Accessible

✓ Loading state

✓ Empty state

✓ Error state

✓ Offline state

✓ Semantic labels

✓ Consistent spacing

✓ Consistent typography

✓ Consistent icons

✓ Dark mode support

✓ Performance optimized

Never consider a screen complete until all checks pass.